1
00:01:24,990 --> 00:01:28,140
[Whispers of Fate]

2
00:01:28,380 --> 00:01:29,950
[Episode 21]

3
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,240
What's going on?

4
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,780
Aren't you scared at all?

5
00:02:03,630 --> 00:02:05,070
Lici, are you really that silly?

6
00:02:05,070 --> 00:02:06,870
Don't you even understand fear?

7
00:02:07,570 --> 00:02:09,280
Forget it. You wouldn't understand anyway.

8
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,740
But there is a kind of sound

9
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:13,940
that you can feel
even if you don't understand.

10
00:02:23,370 --> 00:02:24,780
What is this?

11
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,830
Can I try too?

12
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,560
This is called music.

13
00:02:32,829 --> 00:02:33,160
Here.

14
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:34,600
Try it.

15
00:03:10,329 --> 00:03:11,790
I know what would suit you.

16
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:13,760
Senior has hidden a Mindfast Fox-Dragon.

17
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:14,830
I'll find it for you now.

18
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:15,360
Let's go.

19
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:18,080
What is the Mindfast Fox-Dragon?

20
00:03:18,770 --> 00:03:19,970
It's a real treasure,

21
00:03:20,410 --> 00:03:22,220
a flute that's very difficult to master.

22
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:24,290
What's a flute?

23
00:03:28,450 --> 00:03:29,380
Dinner's ready.

24
00:03:33,850 --> 00:03:35,230
Don't growl at me, little monster.

25
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:35,960
Come with me.

26
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:47,170
Fang Zhou's heart crystal

27
00:03:48,060 --> 00:03:49,500
is now inside my body,

28
00:03:50,850 --> 00:03:51,690
and his body

29
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,900
has been hidden by me in Zhoudi Tower,

30
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,470
preserved in the Immortal Crystal Coffin

31
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,010
[Fang Zhou's Tomb]

32
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:57,600
of the Biluo Palace.

33
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,060
His spiritual essence

34
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,520
and vitality are intact.

35
00:04:01,990 --> 00:04:03,140
As long as I use the Rebirth Scroll

36
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:04,190
to restore it.

37
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,510
Tang Lici.

38
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,560
I'm such a fool.

39
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:26,700
I actually wanted to trust you again.

40
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:51,360
[Zhoudi Tower]

41
00:04:57,480 --> 00:05:00,750
♪ Master ♪

42
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:05,890
♪ You failed to take the Biluo Palace ♪

43
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:10,390
♪ And couldn't kill Tang Lici ♪

44
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:15,560
♪ How dare you go back to your old home? ♪

45
00:05:15,810 --> 00:05:17,000
You really don't take

46
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,430
the Fengliu Shop seriously anymore.

47
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:19,830
I was only gone for 2 days.

48
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:22,660
Can't the Fengliu Shop stay in business
anymore?

49
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,240
Master, since your disappearance,

50
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,370
the Sword Alliance
has made thorough preparations.

51
00:05:26,370 --> 00:05:27,660
Tang Lici has become

52
00:05:27,690 --> 00:05:29,650
the Guest of Honor of the Sword Alliance.

53
00:05:29,650 --> 00:05:31,380
He didn't lose his reputation.

54
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:32,950
Instead, he's become

55
00:05:33,310 --> 00:05:34,480
the most famous marital artist

56
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,280
in the current martial arts world.

57
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:37,950
He's significantly strengthened
the Sword Alliance,

58
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,920
enabling it to amass sufficient fame,
fortune, and influence.

59
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,830
He also has a group of

60
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:42,430
friends willing to die protecting him.

61
00:05:42,430 --> 00:05:43,760
He's now second to none.

62
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,080
But you are

63
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:46,830
notorious in the martial arts world

64
00:05:46,830 --> 00:05:48,690
as the Master of the Fengliu Shop,

65
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:50,870
bringing shame to Zhoudi Tower.

66
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,630
Leader, do you really think

67
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:58,890
Tang Lici is helping the Sword Alliance?

68
00:05:59,409 --> 00:06:00,270
You're sworn enemies.

69
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,870
You can certainly see through him.

70
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:02,680
His next move

71
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,070
is already clear to you.

72
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,480
Tang Lici is merely

73
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,480
using these fools

74
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,040
to deal with the Fengliu Shop.

75
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,120
He wants them to be

76
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:11,270
his pawns and scapegoats,

77
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,000
paving his way to hell.

78
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:15,750
If Tang Lici can use the Sword Alliance,

79
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,920
you can also use me to kill him.

80
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,800
You think I can't kill him?

81
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,920
He is a true monster,

82
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,560
while you're not yet one.

83
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,720
That's why

84
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,510
you can't kill Tang Lici.

85
00:06:30,190 --> 00:06:31,750
You don't do enough good
to be truly virtuous,

86
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,750
nor can you commit great evil.

87
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:34,680
Yan,

88
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,480
with your personality,

89
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,240
you can never reach
the extremes of good or evil.

90
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:38,950
In the end,

91
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:41,390
you're destined to accomplish nothing.

92
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:43,720
Only I can kill Tang Lici!

93
00:06:44,390 --> 00:06:45,590
Whoever touches him,

94
00:06:46,610 --> 00:06:47,930
I will kill them.

95
00:06:50,990 --> 00:06:51,650
As you wish.

96
00:07:11,230 --> 00:07:11,790
Master.

97
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,200
I finally found you.

98
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,120
I'm so worried about you.

99
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,890
Summon everyone to see me.

100
00:07:37,050 --> 00:07:38,380
Hidden-Wing Curse Bug.

101
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:39,960
Using it as eyes and ears

102
00:07:40,370 --> 00:07:41,970
for searching and scouting.

103
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:44,890
What is Liu Yan looking for?

104
00:07:46,030 --> 00:07:47,090
Why did he suddenly

105
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:49,200
return to Zhoudi Tower?

106
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:51,480
Why overthink it?

107
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,270
Let's investigate this Zhoudi Tower,

108
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,330
and we'll find out.

109
00:07:59,330 --> 00:08:00,530
If Liu Yan can't track things down

110
00:08:00,530 --> 00:08:02,330
with the Hidden-Wing Curse Bug,

111
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,020
I can't find anything either.

112
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:06,000
Of course, we need
to ask the puppetry master

113
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,600
Qiaoyi Qiankun to investigate.

114
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,510
He attacked the Biluo Palace

115
00:08:08,510 --> 00:08:10,770
by using up a Sky-Fallen Stone fragment.

116
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,270
He can't continue his research.

117
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,820
Now, apart from the Biluo Palace,

118
00:08:13,820 --> 00:08:15,880
only Puti Valley
possesses Sky-Fallen Stones.

119
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:17,000
If you give him another one,

120
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,930
he'll be eternally grateful to you

121
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:21,360
and willing to do anything.

122
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:22,800
You're right.

123
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,490
I can't believe
I had to remind you of this.

124
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,640
What a fool.

125
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:28,870
You may leave.

126
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:40,070
For what happened in the Qingyang Realm,

127
00:08:40,070 --> 00:08:41,470
thank you, Master Puzhu.

128
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:44,110
I am willing to cooperate

129
00:08:44,310 --> 00:08:45,750
because the Sword Alliance truly

130
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,809
needs Mr. Tang now.

131
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,240
Yielding to circumstances

132
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,150
doesn't mean

133
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,549
I agree with

134
00:08:50,549 --> 00:08:51,679
Mr. Tang's methods.

135
00:08:51,850 --> 00:08:52,480
Same here.

136
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:57,960
Whatever works is a good strategy.

137
00:08:58,250 --> 00:08:59,080
Why would I need

138
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,000
your approval?

139
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,630
Using money to buy loyalty

140
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,460
is not a good start.

141
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:04,710
Without any benefit,

142
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,120
you expect those disciples

143
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,600
to risk their lives fighting evil.

144
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,320
Is that fair?

145
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,370
Using profit as bait

146
00:09:09,370 --> 00:09:10,630
will lead to betrayal for profit.

147
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:12,050
The Evil Pill spreads its poison

148
00:09:12,050 --> 00:09:13,770
precisely because of human greed

149
00:09:13,770 --> 00:09:15,700
and delusions of instant success.

150
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,690
Pursuing benefits and avoiding harm

151
00:09:20,690 --> 00:09:21,900
is human nature.

152
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,910
Isn't it a bit harsh

153
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:25,240
to hold ordinary people

154
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,480
to a sage's standard?

155
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:36,200
This is what they call,
"With great rewards

156
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,130
come brave men."

157
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:39,550
After the news has gotten out,

158
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:40,910
many sects want to join

159
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:43,030
the Sword Alliance's campaign
against the Fengliu Shop.

160
00:09:43,030 --> 00:09:43,720
Moreover,

161
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:46,480
with the court
and the Biluo Palace's support,

162
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:49,080
the entire Sword Alliance's morale
has soared.

163
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,010
I think we should

164
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,790
take advantage while people are willing

165
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:54,080
to fully eliminate
all Fengliu Shop strongholds.

166
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,480
I've already sent Chunji

167
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,210
to lead a reconnaissance team.

168
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:58,670
Master Cheng,

169
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,110
what's your opinion?

170
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:03,140
Eliminating evil completely
is indeed my wish.

171
00:10:05,370 --> 00:10:06,410
But...

172
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,280
Do we have to meet here?

173
00:10:09,390 --> 00:10:10,510
It's so dark here,

174
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,600
making us look like

175
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,660
we're plotting something sinister.

176
00:10:15,650 --> 00:10:17,850
Master Puzhu dislikes crowded places.

177
00:10:18,030 --> 00:10:19,360
The deeper one is in darkness,

178
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:21,200
the more one craves for light.

179
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:24,830
With enemies at our doorstep,

180
00:10:24,830 --> 00:10:26,100
if the Sword Alliance
needs anything in the future,

181
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,760
just send someone to inform me.

182
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,380
I will go to Wanhua Hall

183
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,840
to discuss matters with you.

184
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,390
Great.

185
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,930
I never expected

186
00:10:33,020 --> 00:10:34,690
Master Puzhu to be

187
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:37,180
someone who knows how to be flexible.

188
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,490
To raid Fengliu Shop's strongholds,

189
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:48,620
I'll lead by example

190
00:10:49,190 --> 00:10:50,250
and go ahead first.

191
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:52,750
Perfect.

192
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:54,550
Deputy Lord Yu

193
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:56,870
has just arrived at the Sword Alliance
with his people.

194
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:58,870
I'll go with you to see him.

195
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,360
Master Puzhu,

196
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:03,450
is it really so unbearable for you

197
00:11:03,450 --> 00:11:04,790
to work alongside me?

198
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:06,910
I've heard

199
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,920
that the disciples
of the Tianjing Pavilion

200
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:11,200
must practice meditation and tolerance.

201
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:11,670
How is it

202
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:14,040
that you don't need to practice these?

203
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,520
Farewell. Farewell.

204
00:11:21,570 --> 00:11:23,570
I wish you good luck on your journey.

205
00:11:31,060 --> 00:11:32,020
If Master Cheng

206
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:33,600
also wants to talk about

207
00:11:33,950 --> 00:11:35,190
approval

208
00:11:35,410 --> 00:11:36,410
or other clichés,

209
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:37,750
I already know it.

210
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,000
Perhaps you do have the skills

211
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,870
to fight against the Fengliu Shop.

212
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:44,390
But with your personality,

213
00:11:44,390 --> 00:11:45,790
you can't inherit
the Seven‑String True Tune

214
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:46,790
of Fang Zhou.

215
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,080
Fang Zhou

216
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:55,610
was a man of integrity,

217
00:11:57,090 --> 00:11:58,120
but in the end,

218
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,240
apart from people's respect,

219
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,410
what else did he get?

220
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:07,120
Asking such a question shows

221
00:12:07,790 --> 00:12:10,250
you don't understand
Fang Zhou well enough.

222
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:12,400
I don't want to be Fang Zhou.

223
00:12:12,890 --> 00:12:14,290
You can't be him either.

224
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,240
You're suspected of being Yique Yinyang.

225
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,790
Though after the battle at Biluo Palace,

226
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:31,690
this suspicion was temporarily dispelled,

227
00:12:31,690 --> 00:12:33,620
but with your methods and actions,

228
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:35,030
no one can guarantee

229
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,750
that you won't become the next

230
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:37,750
Yique Yinyang.

231
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:40,080
You are a threat

232
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:41,770
to the Sword Alliance.

233
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:43,270
Tang Lici.

234
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,560
I'll be watching you.

235
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:50,970
You asked me before

236
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:53,000
if I've ever killed the wrong person
with my sword.

237
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,860
Perhaps I have,

238
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,920
but I have no regrets.

239
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,370
For all my mistakes,

240
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:59,390
I will atone in hell.

241
00:13:05,210 --> 00:13:06,410
Why are you laughing?

242
00:13:10,470 --> 00:13:11,630
Master Cheng, your words

243
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:12,870
sound so resolute.

244
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:13,870
Have you

245
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:15,930
moved yourself with your own speech?

246
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:16,920
However,

247
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:19,560
your desire to atone is one-sided.

248
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,250
Have you considered

249
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:23,160
whether those souls in hell

250
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,870
are willing to give you

251
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,270
a chance for redemption?

252
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:00,360
Mr. Tang.

253
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,330
Master Shao, you haven't slept all night.

254
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,690
The turmoil in the jianghu hasn't settled,

255
00:14:07,690 --> 00:14:09,620
making it impossible to rest easy.

256
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:14,800
Forgive my boldness,

257
00:14:14,890 --> 00:14:17,490
are you and the owner of the Fengliu Shop
Liu Yan

258
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:20,210
disciples of the same master?

259
00:14:22,050 --> 00:14:23,780
Chief Fang Zhou of Zhoudi Tower

260
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,720
was our senior.

261
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:29,150
Chief Fang Zhou of Zhoudi Tower

262
00:14:29,150 --> 00:14:30,410
was a man of principle.

263
00:14:30,420 --> 00:14:32,570
My master Jiangnan Feng and he

264
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:35,010
once fought fiercely at Tiandu Peak,

265
00:14:35,010 --> 00:14:37,510
together resisting
Yique Yinyang's rebellion.

266
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:39,970
Mr. Tang,
since you've inherited his legacy

267
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,660
and are willing to join us,

268
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:44,760
you must also have the desire
to help the world.

269
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,120
But my purpose

270
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:48,120
has never been peace in the jianghu.

271
00:14:48,190 --> 00:14:49,720
That's not contradictory.

272
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,790
Didn't you once tell

273
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,080
Master Puzhu

274
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:55,790
that even those with different paths
can work together?

275
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:57,720
As long as our current goals align,

276
00:14:57,790 --> 00:14:59,480
why not journey together for a while?

277
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:01,150
Rest assured,
since we're traveling together,

278
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:02,120
I will handle

279
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:04,310
all Sword Alliance matters properly.

280
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,240
However,

281
00:15:05,670 --> 00:15:07,150
my methods in the future

282
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:09,550
may be even more unacceptable
to ordinary people.

283
00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:11,080
You

284
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,940
might not have peace and quiet
