have his own difficulties.

868
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:51,960
Ms. Zhong.

869
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:55,180
Come with me to a place.

870
00:38:57,590 --> 00:38:58,120
Let's go.

871
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:04,920
The food is ready.

872
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:07,050
And the wine is here.

873
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:09,190
Did you twist your ankle, Miss Shei?

874
00:39:09,190 --> 00:39:09,920
Take it easy.

875
00:39:10,630 --> 00:39:11,320
Ms. Zhong.

876
00:39:15,730 --> 00:39:16,230
Zhong.

877
00:39:16,400 --> 00:39:17,030
Ms. Zhong.

878
00:39:22,510 --> 00:39:23,510
Everyone's here.

879
00:39:26,280 --> 00:39:27,400
Why are you so late?

880
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,590
We've been waiting for you
for a long time.

881
00:39:29,590 --> 00:39:31,590
Shen and I finished our lessons ages ago.

882
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:33,430
Those Sword Masters
kept asking us questions.

883
00:39:33,430 --> 00:39:34,270
They asked me.

884
00:39:34,290 --> 00:39:36,150
You couldn't explain it clearly.

885
00:39:38,030 --> 00:39:38,630
Ms. Zhong,

886
00:39:39,050 --> 00:39:39,980
please sit down.

887
00:39:40,340 --> 00:39:41,340
Come, have a seat.

888
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:51,670
Ms. Zhong, you stood up for justice,

889
00:39:51,050 --> 00:39:56,210
♪ Did you ever wonder then ♪

890
00:39:51,670 --> 00:39:53,270
yet you were punished for it.

891
00:39:53,360 --> 00:39:53,920
I

892
00:39:54,630 --> 00:39:56,280
feel it's completely unfair for you.

893
00:39:56,280 --> 00:40:00,810
♪ As night quietly fell, to ask the moon ♪

894
00:39:56,590 --> 00:39:57,520
But don't worry.

895
00:39:58,000 --> 00:39:59,550
When we battle against the Fengliu Shop,

896
00:39:59,550 --> 00:40:00,730
Yanmen Sect will lead the charge,

897
00:40:00,730 --> 00:40:01,960
and you'll definitely have a chance
to prove yourself.

898
00:40:01,060 --> 00:40:06,150
♪ When the next dawn comes ♪

899
00:40:02,990 --> 00:40:04,190
That's right, Zhong.

900
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:04,920
Take it easy.

901
00:40:05,490 --> 00:40:06,730
I believe you can do it.

902
00:40:06,730 --> 00:40:10,820
♪ Will we too be forgotten? ♪

903
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:10,110
Everyone

904
00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:12,230
will help you return
to the Shanfeng Branch.

905
00:40:11,560 --> 00:40:15,810
♪ The sunlight falls upon you ♪

906
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:16,440
Then

907
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:20,730
♪ Just like when you asked me back then ♪

908
00:40:17,590 --> 00:40:18,390
thank you all.

909
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:21,760
Thank you, Master Jiang.

910
00:40:21,760 --> 00:40:26,460
♪ How do we hide certain answers ♪

911
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:24,440
Thank you,

912
00:40:25,590 --> 00:40:26,280
Mr. Tang.

913
00:40:26,510 --> 00:40:31,160
♪ Those burning moments with you? ♪

914
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:28,960
Ms. Zhong,

915
00:40:29,190 --> 00:40:30,250
no need for thanks.

916
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,240
Fengliu Shop

917
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:33,110
tricked my son into taking the Evil Pill.

918
00:40:31,970 --> 00:40:36,320
♪ The sunlight falls upon you ♪

919
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,460
If it weren't for Ms. Zhong

920
00:40:35,550 --> 00:40:36,550
and everyone else

921
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,840
helping me expose the traitor,

922
00:40:36,670 --> 00:40:41,000
♪ Just like when you asked me back then ♪

923
00:40:39,150 --> 00:40:40,880
Yanmen Sect would be in danger.

924
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,260
Both officially and personally,

925
00:40:42,260 --> 00:40:46,670
♪ How do we hide certain answers ♪

926
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,510
I should help you.

927
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:46,020
Let's not talk about this now.

928
00:40:46,690 --> 00:40:51,980
♪ Those burning moments with you? ♪

929
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:49,160
Let's enjoy this brief moment of peace.

930
00:40:49,230 --> 00:40:50,960
What wine did you bring, Jiang?

931
00:40:51,630 --> 00:40:53,630
This is the finest wine from Yanmen.

932
00:40:54,070 --> 00:40:55,230
Frosty Leaves' Red.

933
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:57,650
A Yanmen specialty, excellent wine.

934
00:40:57,890 --> 00:40:59,760
Paired with Shei's delicious dishes,

935
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:02,030
there is wine and food. Let me try first.

936
00:41:02,030 --> 00:41:02,760
Chi,

937
00:41:03,370 --> 00:41:05,170
don't start eating by yourself.

938
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:06,360
I...

939
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:07,800
It's alright.

940
00:41:08,040 --> 00:41:10,330
Today is a family gathering;
no need for formalities.

941
00:41:10,330 --> 00:41:11,990
Everyone, let's have a toast.

942
00:41:12,380 --> 00:41:17,700
♪ The northern wind hums by my ear ♪

943
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,130
Cheers.

944
00:41:17,990 --> 00:41:22,180
♪ Stirring waves between your brows ♪

945
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:27,960
♪ The flowers scatter in June ♪

946
00:41:28,160 --> 00:41:32,240
♪ I'd rather jump into your soil ♪

947
00:41:33,230 --> 00:41:33,880
Ms. Zhong.

948
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:36,250
Are you unhappy?

949
00:41:37,630 --> 00:41:38,190
No.

950
00:41:39,030 --> 00:41:40,000
I just feel

951
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:42,330
that it feels like ages

952
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:44,320
since I last saw everyone.

953
00:41:45,070 --> 00:41:47,150
The last time we went to Sword King City

954
00:41:47,150 --> 00:41:49,480
seems like it happened in a previous life.

955
00:41:52,140 --> 00:41:53,670
I'd like to toast everyone.

956
00:41:54,550 --> 00:41:55,830
No matter how much time passes,

957
00:41:55,830 --> 00:41:57,690
we should always drink together.

958
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:59,290
You always know what to say.

959
00:42:25,330 --> 00:42:27,530
You seem very happy tonight, Ms. Zhong.

960
00:42:28,120 --> 00:42:29,180
Why is it you again?

961
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:31,710
Do you need something?

962
00:42:31,710 --> 00:42:32,760
I asked you first.

963
00:42:33,180 --> 00:42:34,840
So you should answer me first.

964
00:42:35,030 --> 00:42:36,430
Of course I'm happy.

965
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:37,960
Your turn.

966
00:42:38,220 --> 00:42:39,440
I don't have anything specific.

967
00:42:39,440 --> 00:42:39,880
Why?

968
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:42,490
Can't I chat with you without a reason?

969
00:42:45,310 --> 00:42:46,790
You're so strange.

970
00:42:47,630 --> 00:42:48,760
If you came to the Sword Alliance

971
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:50,090
with other intentions,

972
00:42:50,250 --> 00:42:51,250
I suggest

973
00:42:52,140 --> 00:42:53,420
you leave now.

974
00:42:54,510 --> 00:42:55,970
You're quite perceptive.

975
00:42:56,710 --> 00:42:57,230
Fine.

976
00:42:57,590 --> 00:42:58,390
I'll tell you.

977
00:42:58,990 --> 00:43:00,480
I came to the Sword Alliance

978
00:43:00,480 --> 00:43:01,960
to see

979
00:43:02,150 --> 00:43:04,110
the true face of the fox demon.

980
00:43:05,940 --> 00:43:06,590
Why?

981
00:43:07,260 --> 00:43:07,820
Why?

982
00:43:09,030 --> 00:43:09,760
Because...

983
00:43:10,690 --> 00:43:13,290
Mr. Tang is indeed detestable and hateful,

984
00:43:13,840 --> 00:43:14,960
but I must admit

985
00:43:15,360 --> 00:43:18,000
that he does have a captivating charm.

986
00:43:18,550 --> 00:43:20,150
It makes one unable to resist

987
00:43:20,510 --> 00:43:22,000
falling deeply for him.

988
00:43:25,670 --> 00:43:27,280
You dare to provoke Mr. Tang?

989
00:43:28,280 --> 00:43:30,510
Aren't you afraid
that you'll bring disaster upon yourself?

990
00:43:30,510 --> 00:43:32,880
It's the danger that makes it attractive.

991
00:43:33,230 --> 00:43:33,880
You

992
00:43:33,880 --> 00:43:36,210
understand this feeling best, don't you?

993
00:43:38,150 --> 00:43:40,240
What are you talking about?

994
00:43:41,670 --> 00:43:43,280
What I want to say is,

995
00:43:43,740 --> 00:43:44,960
to get his attention,

996
00:43:45,520 --> 00:43:47,520
you can't follow the ordinary path.

997
00:43:48,630 --> 00:43:50,760
You need to be the most special person.

998
00:43:51,280 --> 00:43:52,920
Don't let yourself need him;

999
00:43:53,290 --> 00:43:55,690
make him need you instead.

1000
00:43:57,380 --> 00:43:59,300
What's between Mr. Tang and me

1001
00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:01,480
is none of your business.

1002
00:44:03,430 --> 00:44:04,510
To be honest,

1003
00:44:04,710 --> 00:44:06,240
I've read your fortune too.

1004
00:44:07,200 --> 00:44:09,840
Your destiny shows weak family bonds

1005
00:44:10,110 --> 00:44:11,510
and no power or wealth.

1006
00:44:12,030 --> 00:44:13,630
What others are born with,

1007
00:44:13,800 --> 00:44:15,230
you must fight desperately to obtain—

1008
00:44:15,230 --> 00:44:17,630
only then might you stand a slim chance
of getting it.

1009
00:44:17,630 --> 00:44:19,490
If you miss just one opportunity,

1010
00:44:20,840 --> 00:44:22,320
you'll lose everything.

1011
00:44:28,070 --> 00:44:29,440
Mr. Fang, do you think

1012
00:44:29,730 --> 00:44:31,260
I would believe your words?

1013
00:44:31,580 --> 00:44:33,170
It doesn't matter if you don't.

1014
00:44:33,170 --> 00:44:34,230
But if I were you,

1015
00:44:34,230 --> 00:44:35,440
with such a fate,

1016
00:44:35,540 --> 00:44:36,480
I would contentedly

1017
00:44:36,480 --> 00:44:37,880
be an ordinary disciple

1018
00:44:38,590 --> 00:44:40,320
and marry a simple, honest man.

1019
00:44:41,110 --> 00:44:42,370
Why struggle for more?

1020
00:44:43,590 --> 00:44:45,320
What if I insist on struggling?

1021
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:50,960
Then I can help you.

1022
00:44:57,460 --> 00:44:58,320
I don't need it.

1023
00:45:02,820 --> 00:45:03,920
Think carefully,

1024
00:45:04,300 --> 00:45:05,170
Ms. Zhong.

1025
00:45:34,240 --> 00:45:35,770
A letter from Shisan Tower.

1026
00:45:36,340 --> 00:45:38,650
The Peach of Three Hues in Pink Attire.

1027
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:41,190
She is Xifang Tao.

1028
00:46:02,490 --> 00:46:04,350
Hand it to Godfather personally.

1029
00:46:05,160 --> 00:46:06,370
Bring back his reply.

1030
00:46:08,690 --> 00:46:11,020
Aren't you going
to ask what this is about?

1031
00:46:12,220 --> 00:46:14,080
I don't have Chi Yun's curiosity.

1032
00:46:14,630 --> 00:46:15,630
The more you know,

1033
00:46:16,030 --> 00:46:17,090
the sooner you die.

1034
00:46:27,370 --> 00:46:28,210
Sometimes,

1035
00:46:29,100 --> 00:46:30,320
the more you know,

1036
00:46:30,880 --> 00:46:32,280
the better your chances.

1037
00:46:33,280 --> 00:46:34,320
Fang Pingzhai,

1038
00:46:34,840 --> 00:46:36,000
your true identity

1039
00:46:36,000 --> 00:46:37,480
is about to be revealed.

